Add AI-Powered CRM Integration to code-server

This patch adds a comprehensive CRM system built with React and shadcn/ui components
that integrates seamlessly with the VS Code interface.

Features:
- Co-pilot Reacher: AI-powered chat assistant
- Home Dashboard: Overview of CRM metrics and activities
- VOIP Dialer: Manual and automated calling system
- Campaigns: Email, SMS, and telemarketing management
- Agent Studio: AI agent building and automation
- Settings: Configuration and user management

